---
import { whatsappUrl } from '../../data/site';

const reveal = 'opacity-0 translate-y-8 transition duration-700 ease-out';
---

<section
  id="inicio"
  class="grid min-h-[calc(100vh-6rem)] gap-6 px-1 py-10 sm:px-3 sm:py-14 lg:grid-cols-[minmax(0,0.95fr)_minmax(560px,780px)] lg:items-center lg:gap-5 lg:py-16 xl:grid-cols-[minmax(0,0.93fr)_minmax(620px,840px)]"
>
  <div data-reveal class={`${reveal} flex max-w-[36rem] flex-col items-start ml-20`}>
    <span class="mb-8 inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-[#fcf2f2] px-4 py-2 text-[0.72rem] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-[#b83737]">
      <svg class="size-4" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
        <path d="M3 12h4l2-5 4 10 2-5h6" />
        <path d="M18 5v4M16 7h4" />
      </svg>
      Excelencia automotriz
    </span>

    <h1 class="m-0 text-[clamp(3.4rem,8vw,5.8rem)] leading-[0.9] tracking-[-0.08em] text-[#b83737]">
      <span class="block font-display font-bold uppercase">NASA</span>
      <span class="mt-2 block text-[clamp(2.6rem,6vw,4.2rem)] font-light italic text-slate-500">Auto Lab</span>
    </h1>

    <p class="mt-7 max-w-[32rem] text-lg leading-[1.75] text-slate-500 sm:text-[1.55rem] sm:leading-[1.7]">
      Ingenieria de excelencia y rigor profesional, con un equipo en constante formacion para proteger y optimizar tu vehiculo con integridad, garantizando un rendimiento de alta calidad.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-10 flex flex-col gap-4 sm:flex-row">
      <a
        href={whatsappUrl}
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[#b83737] px-8 py-4 text-base font-bold text-white shadow-[0_14px_24px_rgba(184,55,55,0.16)] transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:bg-[#a93232]"
      >
        Agendar Cita
      </a>
      <a
        href="#servicios"
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-slate-200 bg-white px-8 py-4 text-base font-bold text-nasa-text transition hover:border-slate-300 hover:bg-slate-50"
      >
        Nuestros Servicios
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div data-reveal style="transition-delay:120ms" class={`${reveal} relative justify-self-end`}>
    <div class="aspect-[1.18/1] w-full overflow-hidden rounded-[2.5rem] shadow-[0_28px_60px_rgba(15,23,42,0.18)] lg:max-w-[760px]">
      <img
        src="/WhatsApp Image 2026-03-21 at 6.06.44 PM.jpeg"
        alt="Vehiculo atendido en NASA Auto Lab"
        class="h-full w-full object-cover"
      />
    </div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-[-1.1rem] left-[-1.1rem] grid grid-cols-4 gap-2 rounded-2xl bg-white/90 p-3 shadow-[0_20px_50px_rgba(15,23,42,0.12)]">
      {Array.from({ length: 12 }).map(() => <span class="size-2 rounded-full bg-[#e7b4b4]"></span>)}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
